Scripts to perform various build, install, analysis, etc operations.

For Windows:
Enable WSL for windows
NOTE: run under wsl environment

setup.sh 
- use to setup development files

build.sh 
- generate package and binaries
- to use:
    cd <scripts directory>
    export ELA_COMPANION=<path to your ela companion parent directory>
    ./windows.sh -o <can linux/windows/macos> -a <can be amd64/arm64/386>

install.sh
- install the system based from package

uninstall.sh
- use to uninstall the system